{"tid":2023963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"突擊雞排妹香閨化妝袋藏安全套　細心為「伴侶」準備男裝tee","createTime":"2020-05-19T10:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T10:49:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c2242e27617964d52f0ce87ce546d028415120db","tid":2023963,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:33:06.000Z","msg":"「雞排妹」鄭家純曾坦承有固定約砲對象，並直言這是成年人的正常需求，又透露發生過關係的男性「50人是最低標準」。有網友搵出今年2月喺節目《綜藝大熱門》嘅片段，節目主持人突擊檢查雞排妹於位南港嘅香閨，喺雞排妹嘅睡房中，主持人最先發現一件男裝tee，當時雞排妹嘅解釋係「如果有些人要過夜的話，要準備一些衣物給他」除咗tee之外，喺雞排妹嘅浴室，亦發現有兩個牙刷，又幾貼心喎。<br />\n<br />\n節目中，其中一個環節係「誰以生活最髒的女人 檢查女藝人包包骯髒程度」，喺雞排妹嘅手袋裡面，主持人除發現一條好臭、有腥味嘅長裙之外，亦有一個有少少發毛嘅化妝袋，雖然吳宗憲一口咬定「沒什麼好看」，但結果當另一主持人沈玉琳打開之後，即時表示：「我不想講，裡面有一個保險套」，而陳漢典則笑言係泡麵嘅調味包，之不過，由於幾位主持人最終都未有拎出化妝袋入面嘅嘢，所以無法確定到底係節目效果，定真有其「套」。<br />\n<br />\n向來敢言嘅雞排妹，除咗曾經透露至今交過手嘅人數至少有50人之外，亦曾自爆發生關係時，最喜歡被對方稱作「小母狗」，認為可以增進感情；此外，佢亦都話過最討厭被床伴問「我跟誰比起來誰比較厲害」、「妳到了沒有。」她舉例過去曾遇過尷尬經驗，對方問：「我跟妳男友誰比較厲害？」她坦言這種情況讓人很為難，「因為你已經是這種情況了，那怎麼會覺得需要問呢？因為這個講出來一定是很傷人的真相。」佢仲奉勸網友都唔好咁問床伴，因為好似出事。"},{"pid":"110ada4c11ae4c6b25eddc192b401e7b78e45437","tid":2023963,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515627/org/0f267295cfc5b2b385457c826c7a9f8e.jpg/3QebBxlyT5_d3TNKr5zz7Fzn7DY5R0UnDqsKDQ6rCg0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4515627%2Forg%2F0f267295cfc5b2b385457c826c7a9f8e.jpg%2F3QebBxlyT5_d3TNKr5zz7Fzn7DY5R0UnDqsKDQ6rCg0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=39e3a4e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n素顏出鏡嘅雞排妹,被發現睡房有男裝tee<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515628/org/cb9d9c62ea5ddb478ec5472c68efba0a.jpg/KiLzm80fQfCc19DnrN7khzEBrDwkqOCEH6xvfB-sb3w?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4515628%2Forg%2Fcb9d9c62ea5ddb478ec5472c68efba0a.jpg%2FKiLzm80fQfCc19DnrN7khzEBrDwkqOCEH6xvfB-sb3w%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=7c0880f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後又被主持人喺化妝袋搵到有安全套。"},{"pid":"ccacefdca799a4bee42f2f08fa7017d53882677c","tid":2023963,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515642/org/c868423595a6f03eec7bbf29889f3ca8.jpg/F0Ar7LXrQOkFliO7U0slebwWg2OrVwIpp_CoKKfwqCg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4515642%2Forg%2Fc868423595a6f03eec7bbf29889f3ca8.jpg%2FF0Ar7LXrQOkFliO7U0slebwWg2OrVwIpp_CoKKfwqCg&h=7eebc52f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515652/org/2955171cea8f037c38fdfd7739741ea2.jpg/5pz_kdN6_zkAcAo5VTAafEl8WfJj_IpNn_9Qy5__UMs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4515652%2Forg%2F2955171cea8f037c38fdfd7739741ea2.jpg%2F5pz_kdN6_zkAcAo5VTAafEl8WfJj_IpNn_9Qy5__UMs&h=4598511b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515649/org/e3f6fdf52d9f7014db3dbbd06197af83.jpg/H1l4AS8Z0glsiaLGb5jOr8-y7asn4nJBGRWl4BkVpeA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4515649%2Forg%2Fe3f6fdf52d9f7014db3dbbd06197af83.jpg%2FH1l4AS8Z0glsiaLGb5jOr8-y7asn4nJBGRWl4BkVpeA&h=27f9457c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515650/org/0bfe25b982e39ef1a7ec4d3a58e7c493.jpg/qetp2vM7Sr0e4GoeLpseUHSYY0uV8YQGyLFqnsixap4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4515650%2Forg%2F0bfe25b982e39ef1a7ec4d3a58e7c493.jpg%2Fqetp2vM7Sr0e4GoeLpseUHSYY0uV8YQGyLFqnsixap4&h=e01f79c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61520be91445954471e82094fe73f6885d2b9849","tid":2023963,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4515651/org/45852529fb5a858df93cb1d8c1c9e7dc.jpg/SxAUvytaeqPFm64XE-GCFXA6rnOEy6TdokTpzKJE6cw\" data-thumbnail-s